# The default build context is unused: the Paheko core is COPYied from the
# paheko_src additional context, not from here. Keep the context empty so the
# whole repo (modules/, doc/, .git…) isn't shipped to the builder.
# (The Dockerfile itself is loaded via the compose `dockerfile:` field and is
# never subject to .dockerignore, so no need to un-ignore it.)
*
